no_background:
  styles:
    card:
      - background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.0)
      - border-width: 0px
display:
  tap_action:
    action: none
  show_icon: false
  show_state: true
  show_label: true
  styles:
    label:
      - color: '#5F5F5F'
    state:
      - font-weight: bold
      - color: '#2F2F2F'
    name:
      - color: '#2F2F2F'
      - font-weight: bold
    grid:
      - grid-template-areas: '".""s" "n""l"'
      - grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr
    card:
      - box-shadow: 'inset -2px -2px 3px #313131, inset 3px 3px 3px black'
      - height: 90px
      - background-color: |
          [[[
            if (states['sensor.stato_allarme'].state === 'Disattivato') 
            return "";
            else 
              return 'rgba(0,9,255,.8)';
          ]]]  
  style:
    .: |
      ha-card {
        background: linear-gradient(23deg, #f8f8e7, rgba(255,0,0,0)  90.71%),
        linear-gradient(207deg,  #f8f8e7, rgba(0,0,255,0) 50.71%);
        margin: 0px 30px 0px 0px;
            }
popup_setting:
  show_icon: false
  styles:
    grid:
      - grid-template-columns: 0fr
      - grid-column-gap: 0.1em
      - grid-template-areas: |
          " icona  n  "      
    card:
      - height: 55px
      - border-bottom-right-radius: 10%
      - border-bottom: 5px solid
      - border-top: 0px solid
      - border-left: 1px solid
      - border-right: 0px solid
      - border-color: var(--paper-slider-active-color)
  state:
    - value: 'off'
      styles:
        card:
          - border-color: var(--paper-slider-container-color)
        name:
          - color: var(--paper-slider-active-color)
  custom_fields:
    icona:
      card:
        type: custom:button-card
        entity: '[[[ return entity.entity_id ]]]'
        show_name: false
        icon: '[[[ return variables.icon || "mdi:home-assistant" ]]]'
        size: 100%
        styles:
          card:
            - height: 56px
            - margin-top: '-10px'
            - width: 40px
            - background-color: GhostWhite
            - border-top-left-radius: 0%
            - border-bottom-left-radius: 0%
            - border-bottom-right-radius: 0%
            - border-top-right-radius: 0%
          icon:
            - color: var(--state-icon-color)
        state:
          - value: 'on'
            styles:
              icon:
                - color: var(--state-icon-active-color)
          - value: 'off'
            styles:
              card:
                - background-color: var(--paper-slider-active-color)
impostazione_allarme:
  template: pressione
  lock:
    enabled: |
      [[[
        if (states['sensor.stato_allarme'].state != 'Disattivato' && 
        states['input_number.control_code_alarm'].state != parseFloat(states['sensor.setting_code'].state)) 
        return 'on' ;          
      ]]]
    unlock: none
  styles:
    lock:
      - top: '-31px'
      - left: 2px
      - padding: 26px
      - color: '#8F8F8F'
    card:
      - height: 40px
      - box-shadow: '-3px -3px 3px #373737, 3px 3px 3px black'
      - width: 65px
      - background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.0)
      - border-width: 0px
    name:
      - color: |
          [[[
            if (states['sensor.stato_allarme'].state != 'Disattivato') {
              return '#8F8F8F';
            } else {
              return '#404040';
            }

          ]]]
      - font-size: 50%
action_type_alarm:
  entity: sensor.stato_allarme
  size: 40%
  color: black
  template: 
    - pressione
    - no_background
  show_icon: false
  state:
    - value: armed_night
      styles:
        name:
          - color: red
  styles:
    card:
      - height: 35px
      - box-shadow: '-3px -3px 3px #373737, 3px 3px 3px black'
      - width: 55px
    name:
      - color: black
      - font-size: 60%
    lock:
      - top: '-24px'
      - left: 2px
      - padding: 18px
      - color: '#8F8F8F'
  lock:
    enabled: |
      [[[
        if (states['sensor.stato_allarme'].state != 'Disattivato'){
        return 'on' ;
        }
      ]]]
    unlock: none
  duration: |
    [[[
      if (states['sensor.stato_allarme'].state != 'Disattivato'){
      return 'on' ;
      }
    ]]]     
aciton_number:
  tap_action:
    action: call-service
    service: script.control_code_alarm
    service_data:
      'n': '[[[ return variables.n  ]]]'
alarm_number:
  color: black
  template: pressione
  styles:
    card:
      - height: 45px
      - box-shadow: '-3px -3px 3px #373737, 3px 3px 3px black'
      - width: 58px
      - background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.0)
      - border-width: 0px
pressione:
  styles:
    card:
      - '--mdc-ripple-color': '#4F4F4F'
      - '--mdc-ripple-press-opacity': 0.2
image_alarm:
  custom_fields:
    back: >
      <svg width="425" height="740" viewBox="0 0 500 520" fill="none" > <rect
      width="555" height="615" fill="url(#pattern0)"/> <defs> <pattern
      id="pattern0" patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox" width="1" height="1">
      <use xlink:href="#image0_1_3" transform="scale(0.002)"/> </pattern> <image
      id="image0_1_3" width="500" height="500"
      xlink:href="data:image/png;base64,"/>
      </defs> </svg>
